description.p:
The composite oxide catalyst in the present embodiment is produced, for example, by the method which includes the following three steps.
(1) the step of preparing raw materials to obtain a raw material-prepared solution;
(2) the step of drying the raw material-prepared solution obtained in the step (1) to obtain a catalyst precursor;
(3) the step of calcining the catalyst precursor obtained in the step (2) to obtain a composite oxide catalyst.
